   - **G2**: Roof by extrusion tool (Ch. 10.2) — ToolId `'roof-by-extrusion'`, hotkey `RE`, grammar state machine (idle→recording→confirm-depth→done), PlanCanvas wiring, createRoof command with extrusionDepthMm
